headline: Prediction: These Could Be the Best-Performing Value Stocks Through 2030
summary: Value stocks have lagged well behind growth stocks in recent years.  D.R. Horton (NYSE: DHI) is the largest homebuilder in the U.S. based on volume -- a status it's held since 2002.  The company operates in 36 states.
